{
  "texts": [
    "These days, the Internet has transformed human life by offering a fast and convenient way to access and share information.",
    "Social networks play a vital role in this process, as they allow users to connect, communicate and exchange content with each other (Zhou and Zafarani 2020).",
    "The Internet and social networks can have positive impacts, such as raising awareness on various issues (from local and global news to citizenship rights and environmental problems), but they also pose challenges regarding the reliability and validity of the information they disseminate.",
    "The absence of regulation and verification on social networks has enabled the rampant spread of disinformation (Zubiaga et al. 2018).",
    "Unfortunately, many users share information without verifying its source or authenticity, often driven by attractive headlines (Bondielli and Marcelloni 2019)."
  ]
}